  <ul class="comments by_rank" >
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="39903755">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/rollingge/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u67340171-704.jpg" alt="如林" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/39903755/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/39903755/" class="">第139页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/rollingge/" class=" " title="如林">如林</a>
                (林无静树 川无停流)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="39903755">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">不过这些城市资本家很早就将其部分利润投资于土地。实际上巩固他们的财产和声望的最好办法是购置土地。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-10-27 23:35</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>不过这些城市资本家很早就将其部分利润投资于土地。实际上巩固他们的财产和声望的最好办法是购置土地。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

